#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:175
#, no-wrap
msgid "XR Unchained"
msgstr "XR Libera"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:178
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Who would have thought that we'd have too many actions  for one newsletter during lockdown? You amaze us, rebels. Keep it up! Please have a read of the full [XR Unchained](https://rebellion.earth/2020/05/20/xr-unchained-14/) for more beautiful and courageous actions we couldn't fit in this issue.* \n"
msgstr "*Chi avrebbe mai detto che una sola newsletter non sarebbe riuscita a contenere tutte le azioni avvenute durante il lockdown? Cari ribelli, non smettete mai di sorprenderci. Continuate così! Potete leggere [XR Libera](https://rebellion.earth/2020/05/20/xr-unchained-14/) per trovare altre meravigliose e coraggiose iniziative che non hanno trovato spazio in questa edizione.* \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:180
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image12.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image12.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:182
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image13.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image13.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:184
#, no-wrap
msgid " *Clockwise from top left: Seebrucke, Dresden, Heidelberg.* \n"
msgstr " *In senso orario, in alto a sinistra: Seebrucke, Dresda, Heidelberg.* \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:186
msgid ""
"In a continuing campaign, German and Austrian rebels have been taking over "
"city parking spaces to **replace cars with planters**, many with built-in "
"bicycle stands. **Urban gardening**, they say, ensures a better quality of "
"life, strengthens social relationships and increases a city's self-"
"sufficiency."
msgstr ""
"In una campagna tuttora in corso, ribelli tedeschi e austriaci hanno invaso "
"i parcheggi della città per **sostituire le macchine con vasi di fiori**, "
"molti con annessi parcheggi per biciclette. Secondo i ribelli, **il "
"giardinaggio urbano** migliora la qualità della vita, rafforza le relazioni "
"sociali e migliora l'autosufficienza della città."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:188
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image14.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image14.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:190
msgid ""
"In the **German city of Saarbrucken** members of XR and Animal Rebellion "
"turned two of the city's fountains a 'poisonous green' colour in order to "
"'make the climate catastrophe visible'. The placard reads 'Climate Politics "
"is Poisoning Us!'"
msgstr ""
"Nella **città tedesca di Saarbrucken** membri di XR e Animal Rebellion hanno "
"tinto le acque di due fontane cittadine di un 'velenoso colore verde' per "
"'rendere visibile la crisi climatica'. La scritta sul cartello recita 'Le "
"politiche sul clima ci stanno avvelenando!'"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:192
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image15.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image15.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:194
#, no-wrap
msgid "**In the UK** rebels in St Ives, Cornwall, have started a **[No Going Back Sundays](https://www.facebook.com/NO-GOING-BACK-Sundays-another-world-is-possible-100121778374234/) movement**. Wearing masks and observing social distancing, they [display home-made placards](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJNV1-Y8dy4&feature=youtu.be) in a prominent local setting every Sunday at 10am. The idea has quickly spread to other parts of the country, and beyond.\n"
msgstr "**Nel Regno Unito** ribelli di St Ives, Cornovaglia, hanno creato una **[Domenica dove non si torna indietro](https://www.facebook.com/NO-GOING-BACK-Sundays-another-world-is-possible-100121778374234/) movement**. Indossando mascherine protettive e rispettando le misure di social distancing, hanno cominciato a [esporre cartelli fatti in casa](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJNV1-Y8dy4&feature=youtu.be) in una famosa località della zona ogni domenica alle 10 di mattina. L'idea si è velocemente diffusa in altre aree del Regno Unito e oltre.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:196
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image16.png)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter39_image16.png)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-05-20-newsletter-39.md:198
msgid ""
"Rebels in **Cambridge and across the UK** also made their streets **bike-"
"friendly** by adding new cycling lanes. Find an [action guide here](https://"
"docs.google.com/document/d/1jBUhJMj59L5XbaJACYyZwekrm29rEYj1exHeBo2ry4Y/edit?"
"usp=sharing) if you want to reclaim your street as well."
msgstr ""
"Ribelli di **Cambridge e in tutto il Regno Unito** hanno reso le strade "
"della città **bike-friendly** creando nuove piste ciclabili. Potete trovare "
"qui la [descrizione dell'attività](https://docs.google.com/document/"
"d/1jBUhJMj59L5XbaJACYyZwekrm29rEYj1exHeBo2ry4Y/edit?usp=sharing) se volete "
"contribuire anche voi a riappropiarvi delle vostre strade."

